    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master the maze, race the clock, and tilt your way to victory! In <strong>Tiltality</strong>, you control  a  maze to guide your ball to the finish flag. Precision and timing are key as you tackle increasingly challenging levels. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play, Improve, Unlock</strong><br>Guide your ball to the finish flag and earn flags by beating challenging levels. The faster you complete a level, the more flags you earn. Collect enough flags to unlock progressively harder levels and other unlockables.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145670/extras/8d42f28199abba40d09290b942101713.poster.avif?t=1750279467\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145670/extras/8d42f28199abba40d09290b942101713.webm?t=1750279467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145670/extras/8d42f28199abba40d09290b942101713.mp4?t=1750279467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create and Share</strong> <br>Unleash your creativity with the level builder. Design your own levels, share them with the community and discover top-rated creations from other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145670/extras/f5c869f366c0a78e98bd87f4a8eb28dd.poster.avif?t=1750279467\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145670/extras/f5c869f366c0a78e98bd87f4a8eb28dd.webm?t=1750279467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145670/extras/f5c869f366c0a78e98bd87f4a8eb28dd.mp4?t=1750279467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Climb the Leaderboards</strong> <br>Compete against players from around the globe. Each Tiltality and user created level comes with a leaderboard, so you can prove your skill and see how you stack up against the best!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
